[[Sahar]] is an [[Iran]]ian/[[Iran|Persian]] name. In farsi Sahar means early morning or dawn. This unique and khafan name means sugar in Russian. Because of the popularity of this name, it has been used in Arabic countries and India to name beautiful girls.

Sahar is also a [[Jewish]]/[[Israeli]] name - it means [[crescent]].

